 \vec{F} = P \hat{\imath} + Q \hat{\jmath}  
 \oint_C P dx + Q dy = \int \int_A \frac{\partial Q}{\partial x} - \frac{\partial P}{\partial y} dA 
P= y-x \rightarrow \frac{\partial P}{\partial y}=1 
Q= 2x-y \rightarrow \frac{\partial Q}{\partial x}=2 
